description	"Shadow Trooper

^2Weaponry:
- Lightsaber
-- ^3Medium ^7/ ^4Fast ^7Styles
-- Saber Defense (3)
-- Blaster Defense (2)
-- Blaster Deflect (2)

^6Inventory:
