^5Force Powers:
- Jump (2)
- Push (2) ^5[CS3]
- Sense (1)
- Grip (2)

^8Attributes:
- Cortosis (1)
- Force Block (2)
- Force Focus (1)

Shadowtroopers met their masters' expectations, to the extent that some stormtroopers feared that they would soon be replaced. Shadowtroopers were first deployed in the Cairn Installation against Kyle Katarn. Several others were stationed on Doomgiver to protect the ship."